description: Fifth and sixth floor extensions, elevational alterations (including balconies and recladding) and change of use of mezzanine and first to fifth floors to 25 one bedroom, 35 two bedroom and 40 three bedroom flats; change of use of ground floor and extension to it for uses within Classes A1, A2, B1, D1 or D2 (Schedule 2, Part 3, Class E of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) Order 1995)
